ns:common.topic.description: Varuq is a village in Shahidabad Rural District, Avaj District, Buin Zahra County, Qazvin Province, Iran. At the 2006 census, its population was 410, in 94 families.

ns:common.document.text: Varuq (Persian: وروق‎, also Romanized as Varūq, Ūrūq, Varagh, Varaq, Vorūq, and Warūq) is a village in Shahidabad Rural District, Avaj District, Buin Zahra County, Qazvin Province, Iran. At the 2006 census, its population was 410, in 94 families.
